data.title: Individuals
data.text: Let me start out, no slight being intended to anyone else, with a link to the web site of my very good friend, Chris Matthew Sciabarra. http://www.nyu.edu/projects/sciabarra/ Chris is a Visiting Professor at New York University and is the editor of Journal of Ayn Rand Studies, as well as author of several books, including Ayn Rand: the Russian Radical and Total Freedom: Toward a Dialectical Libertarianism. In addition to our common interest in things Randian and libertarian, Chris and I both have a deep appreciation of jazz, pop, and film music. His brother, Carl Barry (guitarist, composer), and sister-in-law, Joanne Barry (vocalist), are noted jazz performers in the New York area.
